Author: SaprikMazhik
Title: [ANN][ICO] ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ Cryptune ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ Universal Point of Sale System
Body: Of course, sure. Cryptune POS Software runs in several different terminals depending on the merchants needs, there is VOX-U a terminal that can accept credit or debit card payment as well as Cryptocurrency with a built-in receipt printer, it can also be used wirelessly and can scan QR Codes with ease. There is also VOX-C; if the merchant is only looking for a solution to accept Cryptocurrency payments this is the perfect companion for it, with a built-in receipt printer, it can also be used wirelessly and can scan QR Codes with ease. They also have VOX-Mini a miniature compact bluetooth Credit and Debit card reader that supports Swipe and EMV Card Chips, you can process card payments on the go only using VOX-Mini and your mobile phone with Cryptune Mobile Wallet installed   This is basically from their WP

Author: cryptune
Title: [ANN][ICO] ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ Cryptune ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ Universal Point of Sale System
Body: Hello, Thanks for joining in the conversation, your question is very valid and I'll do my best to address it, What we at Cryptune are implementing to make our coin stay for the long haul is that we are using our CPT token as a reward Token, 3% of every transaction be it FIAT or Crypto (similar to cash-back), these rewards accumulate and then can be later used to buy goods and services. So the more you use the system the more CPT you get and the more you can buy. One thing we want everyone to know is that the CryptunePOS accepts both FIAT and Crypto payments leaving it up to the user which method to use that will benefit them(for instance using perhaps FIAT in the current market).

One, true, integrated payment solution system that incorporates the latest in POS technology along with the ability to accept cryptocurrency payments instantly.  The Cryptune Ecosystem is part of a powerful grassroots movement enticing early adapters of this new technology. Blockchain technology and systems like the Cryptune Ecosystem are viable for global adaptation right now. In the very near future, our goal is for the Cryptune Ecosystem to be a staple for every small business.  Cryptune will overhaul the traditional ways of conducting payment processing and empower small business owners with innovative tools and significantly reduced fees.  CRYPTUNE MISSION   To revolutionize the Point-of-Sale Technology Industry through passion, innovation and our entrepreneurial drive to help businesses of all sizes to succeed with our state-of-the-art POS software combined with lower transaction fees for the user.  Inventory control, sales tracking, real time reporting functionality, text message alerts, easy to use customer contact capabilities and so much more. Cryptuneâ€™s proprietary hardware and software POS system will also allow for the acceptance of over 1000 different cryptocurrencies, including the CPT Reward Token - via our strategic partnership with industry pioneer Coinpayments â€“ bringing the POS market into the next wave of IoT and the web 3.0.   CRYPTUNE FEATURES   â€¢ Total transaction transparency between vendors and consumers â€¢ Substantial savings in fees for vendors and consumers â€¢ Totally secure & fast transactions â€¢ 24 / 7 customer support â€¢ The ability to take over 1000 crypto currencies as a payment method â€¢ Immediate access to transaction payments â€¢ Future Reward Token Program (CPT) for consumers and vendors built on blockchain â€¢ Reward Token (CPT) integration with Coinpayments allowing for access to more than 2.3 million vendors globally â€¢ Global access to your funds via the Cryptune Digital Wallet   OUR COMMITMENT   Our commitment to ourselves, our investors, merchants and consumers is to provide excellent value while delivering the highest quality,holistic POS systems while driving the industry into the coming age of digital currencies and a cashless society.   CRYPTUNE MOBILE DIGITAL WALLET   Cryptuneâ€™s Mobile Digital Wallet is a software program available to Cryptune POS users and CPT Token holders - reward program participants. The wallet is a dynamic mobile payment instrument built for everyday use by all participants in the reward ecosystem.  Users can use it to pay for purchases with the CPT Token, track rewards or use it to hold or pay with other cryptocurrencies including BTC, ETH, LTC, etc. Atomic swap will be implemented to allow for seamless peer to peer transactions between users without incurring heavy fees.  Cryptuneâ€™s Mobile Digital Wallet will allow anyone to transfer funds to friends and family anywhere in the world with no fees incurred when it is sent to and from Cryptune Mobile Wallets.
